[SN]TITLE[SN]
David Perkins: Wigan Athletic midfielder signs new one-year contract

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Wigan midfielder David Perkins has signed a new one-year deal with the League One side.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 34-year-old will play for a third season with the Latics after joining from Blackpool in 2015.
He began his career at Morecambe and has also had spells at Rochdale, Colchester, Chesterfield, Stockport and Barnsley.
"Every squad needs its senior players and David is one of those players every club needs," said boss Paul Cook.
